metadata.description:
Dive into the deep waters of the crypto world with "Whale Talk" by Stockz. This electrifying track blends the worlds of rap and cryptocurrency, creating a unique sound that will have you hooked from start to finish. Get ready to swim with the big money players and experience the thrill of the crypto game, all while jamming to the latest slang word in town - "Whale Talk." Turn up the volume and let Stockz take you on a journey through the world of crypto trap music.

Produced by Fokogoloko
